This post is the recap of my longer article about <a href="https://webdesign.tutsplus.com/articles/css-subgrid-features-syntax-and-the-problem-itll-solve--cms-33038" target="_blank">CSS subgrid</a> published on TutsPlus Web Design that analyzes this question in detail (the two screenshots above are from this piece). It also shows how to perfectly simulate a subgrid without having access to the <code>subgrid</code> value.
